      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "```python\nclass RaftNode:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.term = 0\n        self.voted_for = None\n        self.events = []\n\n    def process_event(self, event):\n        self.events.append(event)\n        if event == 'TIMEOUT':\n            self.term += 1\n            self.voted_for = None\n        elif event == 'VOTE_REQUEST':\n            if self.term == 0:\n                self.term = 1\n                self.voted_for = None\n        elif event == 'HEARTBEAT':\n            self.term += 1\n            self.voted_for = None\n\n    def get_state(self):\n        return self.term, self.voted_for, len(self.events)\n```\nThis class initializes the term, voted-for candidate, and event log, then updates the state based on the event type. It ensures the term increments on timeouts and heartbeats, and handles vote requests by setting the term to 1 if it's zero.",
